Comment: 0,-1:59:55.85,-1:59:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,============正文===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,天空灰蒙蒙的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不知为何城市也变得陌生起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在妈妈面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有哭过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,今后也绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸离开之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈把我该流的泪也一并流光了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有的东西被夺走时才滋生了寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可如果一开始就不曾拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这里一直让我感觉很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,花儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你给世界增添了颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 花儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈跟我说你不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 我们回家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,花儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,突然好难过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为假装坚强的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那个曾给过我温暖的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,又把我一个人丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小绘的头发很柔顺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很适合斜刘海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 小绘
Comment: 0,-1:59:55.85,-1:59:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,---标题---
